parameters.text: This chart displays the % of NPD SKUs that were available in the enrolled stores for the country over a period of last 13 months.
This chart displays the % of NPD SKUs that were available in the enrolled stores for the country for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores that were Pack compliant for the country over a period of last 13 months.
This chart displays the % of NPD SKUs that were available in the enrolled stores for Top Customers within a country for the selected audit date.
This chart lists all the audited NPD SKUs in the country, the % of enrolled stores that they were available for the selected audit date, and the variance in availability from the previous month.
This chart displays the % of NPD SKUs that were available in the enrolled stores across all the Channels in the country for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of 4P, 5P and 6P stores that were Pack compliant for the country for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores that were Pack compliant across all the Channels in the country for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores that were Pack compliant for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of MT enrolled stores that were Pack compliant across all the Product categories in the country for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores that were Pack compliant in different sales regions of the country for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of NPD SKUs that were available in 4P, 5P and 6P stores in the country for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of NPD SKUs that were available in enrolled stores in different sales regions of the country for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of NPD SKUs that were available in MT enrolled stores across all the Product categories in the country for the selected audit date.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores for Top Customers within a country which were Pack Compliant for the selected audit date.
